---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import introImage from "@images/HomeImage2.png";
---

<div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-8">
  <!-- Image below on mobile, left on desktop -->
  <div class="lg:w-1/2 order-last lg:order-first mt-8 lg:mt-0">
    <Image
      src={introImage}
      alt="Cannabis post-harvest facility"
      class="rounded-lg w-full h-auto object-cover shadow-md"
      width={600}
      height={600}
    />
  </div>

  <!-- Text content first on mobile, right on desktop -->
  <div class="lg:w-1/2 space-y-6 order-first lg:order-last">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 leading-tight">
      We specialize in producing premium dried cannabis flowers, backed by a
      pharmaceutical-grade post-harvest facility designed to meet the industry's
      highest standards.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
      <p>
        Our fully automated drying technology enables us to create precise
        curing recipes, ensuring consistency, potency, and top-tier quality in
        every batch.
      </p>

      <p>
        We cultivate CBD, CBG, and THC cannabis flowers, combining innovation
        and expertise to deliver a diverse and refined product portfolio.
      </p>

      <p>
        Our entire infrastructure is EU-GMP compliant, and we have already
        undergone a pre-audit by a specialized EU-GMP firm. While we finalize
        our own EU-GMP certification, we currently supply EU-GMP compliant
        flowers, processed in a facility that meets all regulatory standards as
        non certified flowers.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
